    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "bold": true,
          "text": "Cucurrucucú Paloma"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": "Tomas Mendez Sosa wrote \"Cucurrucucú Paloma\" in 1954, first performed by Lola Beltran. The song is considered a Mexican ranchera classic. The song has been recorded by numerous artists, including Harry Belafonte, Joan Baez, and Pedro Infante. The song was even featured in the 2016 film,"
        },
        {
          "italic": true,
          "text": " Moonlight."
        }
      ]
